data.description: Century Ranch Style home has been in the family for over 55 years offering ENDLESS Possibilities and a One Year Home Warranty* Situated on an “Extra -wide” lot consisting of 3 parcels totaling .32 acres* Conveniently located across the street from Kids Academy of Sheffield Lake* Excellent for those looking for a “simplified lifestyle”* First time buyers, Retirees, Boaters, Investors* Bring your creativity and design to this Gorgeous home* Spacious full bathroom has been updated with a walk-in shower* Eat-in kitchen features an abundance of cabinetry and nice counter space with the appliances staying including the newer stove*Nice size dining room leads to the spacious living room to enjoy visiting with family and friends or invite them outside on the covered back porch* Laundry room complete with washer and dryer*One car garage was turned into a storage building & can be changed back* Because the home was built in 1900 (123 years ago), one of the bedrooms closets are located outside of the bedroom* Situated just steps away from Lake Erie, the City boasts numerous amenities for families and outdoor enthusiasts. In addition to easy access to the lake to watch stunning sunsets, launch a boat, or enjoy a picnic, the city has ten parks- five on the lakefront and has created miles of nature trails enjoyed by walkers or cyclists*POS has been completed* Close proximity to shopping, schools & highways & About 20 miles west of CLE!
